Actions
	TODO			Something we should do
	MAYBE-TODO		Something that we should consider doing
	NOTE			Something we should be aware of and potentially act upon
	HACK			A hack we should fix
	DECISION		We need to make a decision here
	BUG				High priority todo
	TEST			Temporary test item that we should remove
	DEBUG			Temporary debug item that we should remove

	You can view all actions in this project using the command:
		make list-actions

Glossary
	HT 			HomeomorphicTools instance in context.scene.homeomorphictools

	tech-note	Specific note in the tehcnical-details document